  "texts": [
    "ADPO utilizes an internal toxic model, using harmful datasets to enhance safety.",
    "This approach enables the model to assimilate both contextual information and safety criteria derived from toxic data.",
    "Moreover, compared to models trained using DPO, ADPO exhibits higher stability during training across a range of hyperparameters, enhancing optimization based on human preferences while penalizing the generation of unsafe responses.",
    "To the best of our knowledge, this research represents the first adaptation of the DPO algorithm, uniquely employing unsafe data in generative models to incorporate criteria for harmlessness.",
    "In the future, we believe exploring various methodologies for effectively utilizing unsafe data presents a promising avenue for research."
  ],
